\c 15
\s UJesu uphambi kukaPilatu
\p
\v 1 Kwathi khonokho ekuseni kakhulu abapristi abakhulu benza umhlangano kanye labadala lababhali\x + Mat. 27.1. Luka 22.66.\x*, lomphakathi wonke\x + Mat. 5.22.\x*, bambopha uJesu ba\add m\add*qhuba ba\add m\add*nikela kuPilatu\x + Luka 23.1. Joha. 18.28.\x*.
\v 2 UPilatu wasembuza \add wathi\add*: Wena uyiNkosi yamaJuda yini? Wasemphendula wathi kuye: Uyatsho wena.
\v 3 Abapristi abakhulu basebemmangalela ngezinto ezinengi; kodwa yena kaphendulanga lutho.
\v 4 UPilatu wasebuya embuza, wathi: Kawuphenduli lutho yini? Khangela, zingaki izinto abazifakazayo ezimelana lawe.
\v 5 Kodwa uJesu kabesaphendula lutho, waze wamangala uPilatu\x + Mat. 27.11-14. Luka 23.2,3. Joha. 18.29-38.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Langomkhosi wayebakhululela isibotshwa esisodwa, loba yisiphi abasicelayo.
\v 7 Kwakukhona \add umuntu\add* othiwa nguBarabasi, owayebotshiwe lalabo ababevukele umbuso laye, ababebulele ekuvukeleni umbuso.
\v 8 Njalo limemeza ixuku laqala ukucela ukuthi \add enze\add* njengalokho ayehlezi ekwenza kubo.
\v 9 UPilatu wasebaphendula, wathi: Lithanda ukuthi ngilikhululele iNkosi yamaJuda yini\x + Mat. 27.15-26. Luka 23.17-25. Joha. 18.39,40.\x*?
\v 10 Ngoba wayekwazi ukuthi ngomona abapristi abakhulu bamnikele.
\v 11 Kodwa abapristi abakhulu bavusa ixuku, ukuthi kungcono alikhululele uBarabasi\x + Luka 23.5.\x*.
\v 12 UPilatu wasephendula wathi futhi kubo: Pho lifuna ngimenzeni lo elithi uyiNkosi yamaJuda?
\v 13 Basebememeza futhi \add bathi\add*: Mbethele!
\v 14 Kodwa uPilatu wathi kubo: Ngoba wenze ububi bani? Kodwa bamemeza kakhulu \add bathi\add*: Mbethele!
\p
\v 15 Khona uPilatu ethanda ukukholisa ixuku, wabakhululela uBarabasi; kodwa wamnikela uJesu, ese\add m\add*tshaye ngesiswepu, ukuthi abethelwe\x + Joha. 18.40.\x*.
\s Abebutho bamenza uJesu inhlekisa
\p
\v 16 Abebutho basebemngenisa\x + Mat. 27.27-32.\x* phakathi, egumeni\x + Mat. 26.3.\x*, eliyindlu yombusi, basebebizela ibutho lonke ndawonye\x + Mat. 27.27.\x*,
\v 17 bamgqokisa okuyibubende, sebeluke umqhele wameva bamethesa,
\v 18 baqala ukumbingelela \add besithi\add*: Bayethe, Nkosi yamaJuda!
\v 19 Batshaya ikhanda lakhe ngomhlanga, bamkhafulela amathe, baguqa ngamadolo bamkhonza\x + Mat. 8.2.\x*.
\v 20 Sebemklolodele, bamhlubula okuyibubende, bamgqokisa ezakhe izembatho. Basebemusa phandle ukuze bambethele.
\s UJesu esiphambanweni
\p
\v 21 Babamba ngamandla omunye owayesedlula \add othiwa\add* nguSimoni umKurene, evela emaphandleni, uyise kaAleksandro\x + Seb. 19.33. 1 Tim. 1.20. 2 Tim. 4.14.\x* loRufusi\x + Roma 16.13.\x*, ukuthi athwale isiphambano sakhe.
\p
\v 22 Basebemusa endaweni\x + Mat. 27.33-56.\x* \add ethiwa\add* yiGolgotha, okuyikuthi ngokuphendulelwa, iNdawo yokhakhayi\x + Luka 23.33. Joha. 19.17.\x*.
\v 23 Basebemnika iwayini lixutshaniswe lenhlaka ukuthi alinathe\x + Joha. 19.39.\x*; kodwa kalemukelanga.
\v 24 Sebembethele, babelana izembatho zakhe, benza inkatho yokuphosa ngazo, ukuthi ngamunye uzathathani.
\v 25 Kwakulihola \w lesithathu\w**, njalo bambethela\x + Joha. 19.14.\x*.
\v 26 Futhi kwakulombhalo wecala lakhe elalibhalwe phezulu \add usithi\add*: INKOSI YAMAJUDA\x + Mat. 22.20.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Njalo babethela kanye laye abaphangi ababili, omunye ngakwesokunene lomunye ngakwesokhohlo sakhe.
\v 28 Wasugcwaliseka umbhalo othi: Futhi wabalwa kanye lezoni\x + Isa. 53.12. Luka 22.37.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Labedlulayo bamhlambaza, benikina amakhanda abo, besithi: Hiya, wena odiliza ithempeli, ulakhe ngensuku ezintathu,
\v 30 zisindise, wehle esiphambanweni.
\v 31 Langokunjalo abapristi abakhulu labo bakloloda kanye lababhali bathi omunye komunye: Wasindisa abanye, angezisindise yena.
\v 32 UKristu iNkosi yakoIsrayeli kehle khathesi esiphambanweni, ukuze sibone sikholwe. Lababebethelwe kanye laye bamklolodela.
\s Ukufa kukaJesu
\p
\v 33 Kwathi sekufike ihola \w lesithupha\w**, kwaba khona ubumnyama phezu komhlaba wonke kwaze kwaba lihola \w lesificamunwemunye\w**.
\v 34 Ngehola lesificamunwemunye uJesu wamemeza ngelizwi elikhulu, wathi, "Eloyi, Eloyi, lama sabaktani?" Okuyikuthi ngokuphendulelwa: Nkulunkulu wami, Nkulunkulu wami, ungitshiyeleni\x + Hlab. 22.1.\x*?
\v 35 Labanye kwababemi khona besizwa bathi: Khangelani, ubiza uElija.
\v 36 Wasegijima omunye, wagcwalisa uzipho ngeviniga, waluhloma emhlangeni, wamnika ukuthi anathe, esithi: Yekelani, sibone uba uElija uzakuza amethule.
\v 37 UJesu wasememeza ngelizwi elikhulu waphefumula okokucina\x + Luka 23.46.\x*.
\p
\v 38 Leveyili lethempeli ladatshulwa \add laba zincezu\add* ezimbili laqala phezulu lisiya phansi.
\v 39 Kwathi induna yekhulu eyayimi maqondana laye ibona ukuthi ukhale njalo, waphefumula okokucina, yathi: Ngeqiniso lumuntu ubeyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 27.54. Luka 23.47.\x*.
\p
\v 40 Kwakukhona labesifazana bebukele bekhatshana, okwakukhona phakathi kwabo loMariya Magadalena, loMariya unina kaJakobe omncinyane lokaJose, loSalome,
\v 41 (labo abamlandela, eseseGalili, bamsebenzela), labanye abesifazana abanengi abenyukela eJerusalema\x + 16.1. Mat. 27.56.\x* laye.
\s Ukungcwatshwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 42 Kwathi sekuhlwile\x + Mat. 27.57-61. Luka 23.50-56. Joha. 19.38-42.\x*, ngoba kwakungamalungiselelo, okuyikuthi usuku phambi kwesabatha\x + Mat. 27.62.\x*,
\v 43 wafika uJosefa owayevela eArimathiya, ilunga\x + Luka 23.50.\x* elihloniphekayo\x + Seb. 13.50; 17.12.\x* lomphakathi, owayelindele laye umbuso kaNkulunkulu\x + Luka 2.25.\x*; wangena ngesibindi kuPilatu, wacela isidumbu sikaJesu.
\v 44 UPilatu wasemangala ngokuthi usefile; wabizela kuye induna yekhulu, wayibuza ukuthi kambe sekuyisikhathi efile.
\v 45 Esazisiwe yinduna yekhulu, wamnika uJosefa isidumbu\x + 15.39.\x*.
\v 46 Wasethenga ilembu elicolekileyo, wamethula, wamgoqela ngelembu elicolekileyo, wambeka engcwabeni elaligujwe edwaleni; wagiqela ilitshe emnyango wengcwaba.
\v 47 Futhi uMariya Magadalena loMariya \add unina\add* kaJose babona lapho abekwe khona\x + Luka 23.55.\x*.